00:06:04.269 --> 00:06:12.779
because they're his, really, our speech should reflect his view,

00:06:12.779 --> 00:06:17.779
keeping in mind that we're included in these imperfect children

00:06:17.779 --> 00:06:21.779
that he overlooks the shortcomings of.

00:06:21.779 --> 00:06:26.779
The Bible realistically says, we all stumble many times,

00:06:26.779 --> 00:06:29.779
not once in a while, many times.

00:06:29.779 --> 00:06:32.779
